{"tid":1285595,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一張圖KO林鄭連橫之計","createTime":"2019-07-04T15:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T16:05:36.000Z","uid":37232,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"23eb21fffe9f6f4b9b4fc51faa69784fb0af7092","tid":1285595,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Xz7BkY70DJI/TvhudknmVQI/AAAAAAAAJL0/5qJLrkgrLpk/s1600/z3HxT2lNcKmAyxaXXdiELw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Xz7BkY70DJI%2FTvhudknmVQI%2FAAAAAAAAJL0%2F5qJLrkgrLpk%2Fs1600%2Fz3HxT2lNcKmAyxaXXdiELw.jpg&h=a23eefd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78c381787ea281cb6d63e17d7ae3fc07f6a1a24d","tid":1285595,"uid":37232,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"雖然陳雲成日唔食藥但今次OK...<br />\n大學學生會最多只可以話轉達訴求, 無得談判, 亦唔可能控制民間運動<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：切勿談判、拒絕代表、不信承諾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285599</a><br />\n<br />\n一、切勿談判：絕對不可進入任何拖延時間而令自己情緒平復及場地局部恢復日常秩序而令在場者被瓦解及司法報復的談判。不要以台灣的太陽花運動為榜樣，而那是個失敗的運動。<br />\n<br />\n二、拒絕一切代表：絕對不可以信任任何議會代表或民間代表。任何人如果代理這場談判，都會冒著難以估計的政治道德風險，因為你面對的是毫無原則的、隨時背信棄義的中共及港共。<br />\n<br />\n三、不可信任任何政府元首或政府部門的口頭承諾，這些是政府的城下之盟，他們可以隨時反悔而撲殺而毫不影響政府的道德立場。<br />\n<br />\nFrom Wan Chin"},{"pid":"f617ec03d9dd466950915fe2a0bd7db8e21f09cf","tid":1285595,"uid":37232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:59:05.000Z","msg":"林鄭背後D軍師都好撚毒"},{"pid":"d39da31c258b4e9b7970c0a22b5ad1e7770abbd7","tid":1285595,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"淋病仆街死"},{"pid":"47f0d9b1ae1051f7354417405023c70419284be2","tid":1285595,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86%E5%9B%8D%E5%B8%96%E8%A1%97-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E9%81%8B